</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Your test system already contains several predefined <a href="/en/crm/sending-emails#1200">email templates</a>. The email template <strong>Confirmation of store order</strong> is used as an example for how to customise email templates to meet your needs.</p>
</div>
