<p>Click on <strong>Homepage</strong>.<br>
→ The preview area of the homepage opens.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Move elements via Drag&amp;Drop from the left side into the preview area. Pay attention to the information given in <a href="#table-elements-shop-builder">Table 11</a>.<br>
→ New elements are added below the existing ones.</p>
