<div class="sect4">
<h5 id="650">Setting up the customer area</h5>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Adjust the <strong>My account</strong> area for your customers in the <strong>Checkout and My account</strong> tab. Additionally, set up <a href="/en/online-store/online-store/setting-up-ceres#430">returns</a> for your online store in this tab.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph instruction">
