<div class="sect4">
<h5 id="660">Entering SEO meta data</h5>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>In the <strong>SEO</strong> tab you find settings for optimising your online store for search engines. Here, you control access to your static online store pages by robots.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph instruction">
<p>Carrying out settings for search engine optimisation:</p>
</div>
<div class="olist arabic">
<ol class="arabic">
<li>
<p>Go to <strong>Plugins » Plugin overview</strong>.<br>
→ The plugin overview will open.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Click on <strong>Ceres</strong>.<br>
→ The plugin will open.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Click on <strong>Configuration</strong> in the directory tree.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Click on the <strong>SEO</strong> tab.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Carry out the settings. Pay attention to the information given in <a href="#table-seo-settings">Table 16</a>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>Save</strong> the settings.</p>
</li>
</ol>
</div>
<table id="table-seo-settings" class="tableblock frame-all grid-all stretch">
<caption class="title">Table 16. Carrying out settings for search engine optimisation</caption>
<colgroup>
<col style="width: 25%;">
<col style="width: 75%;">
</colgroup>
<thead>
<tr>
<th class="tableblock halign-left valign-top">Setting</th>
<th class="tableblock halign-left valign-top">Explanation</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Robots for homepage</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Select <strong>All</strong>, <strong>index</strong>, <strong>nofollow</strong>, <strong>noindex</strong> or <strong>nofollow, noindex</strong> to control access to the homepage of your online store by robots. Values of the meta element Robots are analysed by search engine crawlers. These values determine how crawlers deal with the page and any links on that page.<br></p>
